'''StarlightLab''' is a world created by Bia_Kawaii_Br for [[Space_Jam_2026|Space Jam 3]]. The world was designed around a space exploration theme, reflecting the creator's interest in the subject.

== Design ==
StarlightLab was created for [[Space_Jam_2026|Space Jam 3]]. Players begin with a simulated moon landing, arriving at a functional dome base on the lunar surface.

The dome is divided into two main sections. One side contains a living area with a cinema room, kitchen, lounge, and private bedrooms overlooking the lunar surface. The other side contains gameplay features, including a space vehicle customization system, mission tracking, an achievement system, and helmet personalization — the helmet activates automatically when players leave the dome to explore the 15km² exterior map, which includes ramps, time trial races, and hidden areas.

== Map overview ==
* '''Living spaces''': The dome includes a kitchen, cinema room, and lounge area for socializing.
* '''Private bedrooms''': Rooms with a view of the lunar surface, available for avatar rest.
* '''Exploration & progression''': Players can customize their vehicle and helmet, accept missions, and track progress before venturing outside.
* '''[https://vrchat.com/home/group/grp_fa1b4dab-3c39-4dfc-b5ed-9453e3d20b9c/store VIP area]''': A private area available to select players.
* '''Game room''': A dedicated area with activities for various playstyles.
* '''Cinema/media room''': A shared space for watching videos and films.
* '''Time trial races''': Competitive races held on the lunar surface using exploration vehicles.

== Performance ==
StarlightLab is optimized to run on low-to-mid range PCs without significant loss of visual quality.